branchCategory.name: C96Y(D), ISO 15552 Cylinder, Smooth Cylinder, Double Acting, Single Rod
branchCategory.description: Series C96 cylinders conform to ISO 15552.  The series is available with a single or double rod in 6 bore sizes from ø32 to ø125mm.  High accuracy covers and tie rod nuts improve mounting accuracy and extend the cylinder life.  Increasing the precision of the bushing and piston rod, as well as reducing tolerances, has decreased the deflection of the piston rod.  Standard strokes range from 25 to 1000mm.
